Question: How can we combine Pango image creation with a for loop? [Be specific]
 We can combine a far loop to a pango image by adding it in the beginning before
  convert and list all the variables we want to add in. 


How will this help us create, more better art?
 This will help us create better art by making many pictures at a time
  with something different between them, and letting select what image we
   like the most out of the group.
